{"tid":225072,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"［筍工出沒］微軟香港增假期福利","createTime":"2017-05-01T13:43:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-02T07:07:40.000Z","uid":38544,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"76a7cc8d79dca67cc2c46a2708a2ffe26da157ea","tid":225072,"uid":38544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T13:43:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u8cZ34Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu8cZ34Y.jpg&h=19a52ce2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"000c6f568cab893b785ae151ab529e70b8f9b612","tid":225072,"uid":38544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T13:45:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u8cZ34Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu8cZ34Y.jpg&h=19a52ce2&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n繼渣打銀行及香港寬頻後，微軟今日宣布香港的員工福利升級。最新安排是<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">女士產假由10星期增加至20星期，男士侍產假由3日跳升至6星期</span></span>，可於1年內最多分2次放取。另新推6星期有薪領養假，不分男女，可於1年內分最多分兩次放取。<br />\n<br />\n申請親人看護假 講個信字 <br />\n<br />\n產假、侍產假、領養假未必人人用得到，但同是新推的親人看護假(Family Caregiver Leave )就惠及各年齡員工。每年可享4星期有薪親人看護假，照顧子女、自己及配偶的祖父母、父母、兄弟姊妹。<br />\n<br />\n微軟香港人力資源總監許珮雯表示：「基於信任原則，沒有硬性規定同事提交證明。同事與直屬上司商討後，就可放取。」她指公司沒規定哪些病才可申請，如長者跌倒需長時間照顧，也可申請，不一定是非常嚴重的病。「我們相信，同事不會以親人的病來開玩笑。」<br />\n<br />\n許珮雯指，科技行業都希望吸引更多女性及多元化人才加入，但很多人也擔心繁忙的工作未必能兼顧家庭，增加以上福利有利吸引更多人才。今次福利升級是全球性行動，香港屬於第一批實行地區，比美國更早。「有工會的地方，要先與工會商討再實行。」<br />\n<br />\ndaddy都有得放個半月好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52087f7a2db64b6adcaaaee22c18b6d99d446644","tid":225072,"uid":38544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T13:48:08.000Z","msg":"至於近日微軟香港開始推行一項新福利，身為準媽媽的員工Angie就表示歡迎，她認為20星期的女士產假對媽媽來說，在生理及心理上都有充足時間去復原，加上公司彈性上下班時間，在上司同意下，員工可以留在家中工作，方便照顧初生嬰兒，<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">另外公司亦設有育嬰室方便在職媽媽使用。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n公司設有育嬰室<br />\n即係可以帶埋BB返公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86d6e7d06f2e53c1082bfba357ac7628ece008c7","tid":225072,"uid":38544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T14:11:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/money18/videos/10155274399991552/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fmoney18%2Fvideos%2F10155274399991552%2F&d=h9s%2FmsO%2BhBO0acKdDJaYEU%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=cdcbbb3f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/money18/videos/10155274399991552/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nMicrosoft微軟上周公布的第3季業績，盈利按年升28%至48億美元，雖然略遜預期，但集團的股價早前就不斷創新高，這間全球員工逾10萬名的全球電腦軟件巨擘，香港區辦公室係點樣？他們的科技又可以怎樣幫助零售商去營運？即刻Click入<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2oOqf1w用360度視角睇吓喇！\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2oOqf1w%E7%94%A8360%E5%BA%A6%E8%A6%96%E8%A7%92%E7%9D%87%E5%90%93%E5%96%87%EF%BC%81&d=h9s%2FmsO%2BhBO0acKdDJaYEU%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=47fa0659\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2oOqf1w用360度視角睇吓喇！</a>"},{"pid":"c23e083ebf1fbe905b3efbb94de86a887c47048e","tid":225072,"uid":59700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T14:17:08.000Z","msg":"硬就硬 軟就軟<br />\n咩撚野叫微軟"},{"pid":"0f6caa59a98eca2e5f32e4c343b900bece163473","tid":225072,"uid":68079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T14:45:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>硬就硬 軟就軟<br />\n咩撚野叫微軟</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8922519c3901a9be9da1c52169c35b54905a2aad","tid":225072,"uid":38544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T00:29:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>硬就硬 軟就軟<br />\n咩撚野叫微軟</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=